# Changelog

## 0.7.3 (packaged)

- Initial Cloudron package: rebase upstream `ghcr.io/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw:debian` onto `cloudron/base:5.0.0`.
- Gateway on port 42617, `healthCheckPath` `/health`, persistent `/app/data`.
- Seeded config with `require_pairing = true` for internet exposure.
- Enable `postgresql` addon and wire ZeroClaw memory to it (`[memory] backend = "postgres"`, `start.sh` exports `ZEROCLAW_POSTGRES_URL` from `CLOUDRON_POSTGRESQL_URL`).
- Upstream release notes: https://github.com/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw/releases/tag/v0.7.3
